# Naming alias — same template as docker.ulnovatech.env.example
#
# The Oracle deploy plan uses "ulnovatech.env" in docs; Docker Compose mounts
# infra/env/docker.ulnovatech.env on the VM. Use either name on disk; only the
# path passed to ULNOVATECH_ENV_FILE matters.
#
# Canonical template:
#   infra/env/docker.ulnovatech.env.example
#
# On the server:
#   cp docker.ulnovatech.env.example /opt/ulnovatech/env/docker.ulnovatech.env
#
# Do not commit live .env files (see repo .gitignore).
